ygData.msgSnippet: Interesting.  Do you know the name of the Iksar NPC?  How long does it take him to kill Feydedar?  Just wait till its near dead 45 seconds from dead have a 60
ygData.messageBody:
Interesting. Do you know the name of the Iksar NPC? How long does it take
him to kill Feydedar? Just wait till its near dead 45 seconds from dead
have a 60 enchanter Dictate the Iksar and loot up. But the Iksar is prob
too high to do that with.


Mu
